	<h2>2.1 Найдите правильные ответы на вопросы. </h2>
	<ol>
		<li>Wheres the camera? In your bag</li>
		<li>Is your car blue? No, it's black</li>
		<li>Is Kate from London? No, she's Ameгican.</li>
		<li>Am I right? No, l'm not</li>
		<li>Wheres Amy from? London</li>
		<li>What colour is your bag? Black.</li>
		<li>Are you hungry? Yes, you are</li>
		<li>How is George? Very well</li>
		<li>Who's that woman? My sister</li>
	</ol>
	<h2>2.2 Составьте вопросы с этими словами. </h2>
	<ol>
		<li>Are your parente at home</li>
		<li>How is your mother</li>
		<li>You job is interesting</li>
		<li>Are thase seats free</li>
		<li>Where are you from</li>
		<li>Are you a student</li>
		<li>The station is near here</li>
		<li>Are your children at school</li>
		<li>Why are you sad</li>
	</ol>
	<h2>2.3 Допишите вопросительные предложения. Используйте What ... / Who ... / Where ... / How .... </h2>
	<ol>
		<li>How are your parents? Theyr'e fine, thank you.</li>
		<li>Where is the bus stop? At the end of the street.</li>
		<li>What meed your childen? Five, six and ten.</li>
		<li>What is the time? 6 o'clock.</li>
		<li>Whar is your favourite sport? Skiing</li>
		<li>Who is the man in this photo? Thats my father.</li>
		<li>What color is your new shoes? Black.</li>
	</ol>
	<h2>2.4 Напишите вопросы. </h2>
	<ol>
		<li>Whats your name? Paul.</li>
		<li>Where are you American? NO, I'm Australian</li>
		<li>How old are you? I'm 30.</li>
		<li>What is a teacher? No, l'm а lawyer. </li>
		<li>Where is she from? Shes Italian.</li>
		<li>Whats is her name? Anna</li>
		<li>How old are she? Shes 27</li>
	</ol>
	<h2>2.5 Напишите краткие ответы (Yes, 1 am. / No, he isn't. и т. д.). </h2>
	<ol>
		<li>Are you American? No, I not.</li>
		<li>Are you thirsty? Yes, I am.</li>
		<li>Is your father at work? Yes, he at work.</li>
		<li>Are your hands cold? No, I not</li>
		<li>Is it Monday today? Yes, today Monday.</li>
		<li>Are you a teacher? Yes, I'm a teacher.</li>
	</ol>
	<h2>2.6 Переведите предложения на английский язык. </h2>
	<ol type="|">
		<li>Вы англичанка? --- Are you English?</li>
		<li>Ваш брат дома? --- Is your brother at home?</li>
		<li>Где Марина и Том? --- Where is Marina and Tom?</li>
		<li>Сколько тебе лет? --- How old are you?</li>
		<li>Как тебя зовут? --- What's your name?</li>
		<li>Откуда Бен? --- Where is Ben from?</li>
		<li>Где мой телефон? --- Where's my phone?</li>
		<li>Какого цвета твои глаза? --- What colour are your eyes?</li>
		<li>Кто тот мальчик? --- Who is that boy?</li>
		<li>Почему ты здесь? --- Why are you here?</li>
	</ol>
 
